('1', 'aviary-project', 'aviary-project', 'wp-content/gallery/aviary-project', 'Aviary Project', 'The aviary then transferred my Birdcage into a physical topography at a very large scale.The pavilion found within the aviary was made to look like an extension of the hillside creating a familiar habitat for this merged bird (see Bird Composition). The merged bird can then interact with the other birds in the aviary on the cantilevered section of the pavilion. People who wish to view the birds must travel up the stairs surrounded by waterfalls to reach this cantilevered section.\r\n', '0', '14', '3'),
('2', 'birdcage', 'birdcage', 'wp-content/gallery/birdcage', 'Birdcage', 'The birdcage represents the internal structure of a merger between three birds. The use of rib cages represents the idea of a cage found within a bird that anchors it in its physical form. This is the 3rd project in a series of 4 which all began with a drawing of a bird. The birdcage is bent steel wire soldered together to create rib cage like structures.', '0', '18', '3'),
('3', 'birds', 'birds', 'wp-content/gallery/birds', 'Birds', '3 drawings of the same bird in flight and 1 drawing of the 3 bird drawings superimposed', '0', '0', '3'),
('4', 'freehand_drawing', 'freehand-drawing', 'wp-content/gallery/freehand_drawing', 'Freehand Drawing', 'Some of my more polished works that were completed in Freehand Drawing 1 at McGill University', '0', '34', '3'),
('5', 'sketches', 'sketches', 'wp-content/gallery/sketches', 'Sketches', 'Sketches from Freehand Drawing 1', '0', '48', '3'),
('6', 'sketchbook', 'sketchbook', 'wp-content/gallery/sketchbook', 'Sketchbook', 'Concept and Investigatory drawings used to create my Aviary project', '0', '56', '3'),
('7', 'wind-up-bird-chronicles', 'wind-up-bird-chronicles', 'wp-content/gallery/wind-up-bird-chronicles', 'Wind Up Bird Chronicles', 'Artwork Produced by interpreting a passage for the book \\&quot;Wind-up Bird Chronicle\\&quot;', '0', '59', '3'),
('8', 'pavilion-wind-up-bird-chronicle-pavilion', 'pavilion-wind-up-bird-chronicle-pavilion', 'wp-content/gallery/pavilion-wind-up-bird-chronicle-pavilion', 'Pavilion - Wind-Up Bird Chronicle Pavilion', 'A three dimensional building created from and only from the three drawings regarding the wind up bird chronicle', '0', '65', '3');
