ta\";s:7:\"suggest\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"http://www.websitedefender.com/?p=1545\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:381:\"WebsiteDefender has been designed from the ground-up to provide a robust security solution to the 50 million (and counting) users of WordPress sites and blogs. WordPress has proven itself as the Web&#8217;s biggest and most successful community-driven blogging platform, which is why we are reaching out to WebsiteDefender&#8217;s community of users to contribute their ideas [...]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Jacques G\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2489:\"<p><a href=\"http://www.websitedefender.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebsiteDefender</a> has been designed from the ground-up to provide a robust security solution to the 50 million (and counting) users of <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress</a> sites and blogs. WordPress has proven itself as the Web&#8217;s biggest and most successful community-driven blogging platform, which is why we are reaching out to WebsiteDefender&#8217;s community of users to contribute their ideas and help shape the future of the service.</p>\n<h2>Have a say in how your site is protected</h2>\n<p>Although still in beta stage, WebsiteDefender has already massed a following of over 10 thousand active users, so it&#8217;s time your voices are heard. For the uninitiated, browse to <a href=\"https://dashboard.websitedefender.com/register-for-free-website-scan.php\" target=\"_blank\">https://dashboard.websitedefender.com/register-for-free-website-scan.php</a> to start securing your site for free using WebsiteDefender. The process is quick and simple and you will need FTP access to upload the agent file to your site which will actively monitor it for threats. After taking WebsiteDefender for a spin, navigate to <a href=\"http://ideas.websitedefender.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://ideas.websitedefender.com</a> to start contributing to the pool of ideas and suggestions. To get you started, here are a few good reasons to jump on the ideas bandwagon:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The <a href=\"http://ideas.websitedefender.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebsiteDefender Ideas</a> platform is the best way to ensure we are instantly aware of your ideas and suggestions</li>\n<li>Vote for other ideas suggested by community members to increase their chance of being included in future WebsiteDefender builds</li>\n<li>Watch the evolution of WebsiteDefender in realtime as the most popular ideas float to the top</li>\n<li>Subscribe to the feed of ideas to learn how other WordPress users would like to secure their sites</li>\n<li>Subscribe to the comments feed for your idea to see what other users have to say about your idea</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We look forward to learning more about how you think WebsiteDefender can put your mind at rest by keeping your site secure. Don&#8217;t forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WebsiteDefender\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> and <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/WebsiteDefender\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> to remain in touch; and don&#8217;t forget to spread to word.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"http://www.w