('611', '3', '2011-08-29 10:19:20', '2011-08-29 14:19:20', '<p>During my time at <a href=\"http://www.hc-sc.gc.ca/index-eng.php\">Health Canada</a> I was added to the PeopleSoft Project. Our primary function was to oversea the migration from HR Advantage and the deployment of <a href=\"http://www.oracle.com/us/products/applications/peoplesoft-enterprise/index.html\">PeopleSoft</a>. Within this project my primary function was to create the organizational structure within PeopleSoft that would be the skeleton structure that would accept the migrated data. The two primary components that I worked with were the <a href=\"http://www.canada.gc.ca/depts/major/depind-eng.html\">Department Tree</a> structure as well as the <strong>Location Codes</strong> of the Health Canada and <a href=\"http://www.phac-aspc.gc.ca/index-eng.php\">Public Health Agency of Canada</a> facilities.</p>', 'PeopleSoft', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '109-revision-2', '', '', '2011-08-29 10:19:20', '2011-08-29 14:19:20', '', '109', 'http://www.jacobhooey.com/109-revision-2.html', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),
('567', '3', '2011-08-23 14:59:08', '2011-08-23 18:59:08', '<p>\r\nThis portfolio was created from artwork that was completed while at Bishops University and a couple pieces of my earlier work. I used this collection of artwork to gain admittance in the McGill University Architecture program. The most difficult and interesting piece of art in this portfolio was the Hologram, which was developed in my Physics Lab class and took almost a semester to complete. This portfolio contains some of my best work and I plan on continuing to use it to showcase my artistic talent.\r\n</p>\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<p>\r\n[gview file=\"http://www.jacobhooey.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/McGill-Entrance-Portfolio.pdf\"]\r\n</p>', 'McGill Entrance Portfolio', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '488-revision-3', '', '', '2011-08-23 14:59:08', '2011-08-23 18:59:08', '', '488', 'http://www.jacobhooey.com/488-revision-3.html', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),
