('659', '3', '2011-09-26 15:53:40', '2011-09-26 19:53:40', '<p>Thank you for visiting JacobHooey.com. This is my first professional site and it is an online resume constructed in blog format. I have different areas of my life published here, from my professional resume to my personal artwork. I also create posts describing unique <a href=\"http://www.jacobhooey.com/category/skills\">skills</a> that I have developed over the years. </p>\r\n<p>\r\nBefore you start exploring let me tell you a bit about myself. I graduated from Bishop\'s University with a Bachelors of Science specializing in Physics and mathematics. While completing my degree I realized I had a real passion for computer programming and I started to expand my knowledge in my spare time. Now I can code in Java, FORTRAN, HTML, CSS, php,<a href=\"http://www.jacobhooey.com/asp-ldap.html\"> asp</a> and I am currently learning C/C++. I am hoping to work for a video game company some day where I can apply my love of programming, gaming and designing all into one career. \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nAfter Bishop\'s University I moved into a more artistic education stream at McGill University as an Architecture student. Here I learned how to release my creativity using different artistic mediums. I only completed one semester before realizing that architecture was not my passion, but I continue to carry with me all the skills I developed in drawing and spatial analysis.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nNow I am expanding my knowledge of computers and the corporate environment through hard work and determination. Each new job I take provides me with a new set of skills, from Quality Assurance to Technical Support. I  have great critical thinking skills which allow me to pick up projects quickly and I work hard to see them to completion. If you wish to ask me some questions or want to offer me a job you can contact me at <a href=mailto:\"info@jacobhooey.com\">info@jacobhooey.com</a>\r\n\r\n', 'Welcome', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '31